emails.subject: Partnership Discussion - AI Integration
emails.body: Hi, following up on our conversation at the AI summit last month. We're very interested in exploring a partnership around your AI agents platform. Our CTO, David Park, would love to schedule a deeper dive into how we might integrate your technology with our enterprise suite. Are you available next week for a 30-minute call?

emails.subject: RE: API Access Request - Sandbox Environment
emails.body: Thanks for granting us sandbox access. Our engineering team has been testing the API endpoints and we're impressed with the response latency. We've run initial benchmarks and the results look promising for our use case. Let's discuss next steps for a pilot program. I'll loop in our VP of Product, Maria Santos, for the next meeting.

emails.subject: TechCorp x Our Company - Pilot Proposal
emails.body: Following our initial discussions, I'd like to propose a 3-month pilot program. We would integrate your AI agent capabilities into our customer support workflow, targeting a 30% reduction in ticket resolution time. Budget for the pilot has been pre-approved by our leadership. Can we discuss scope and timeline?

emails.subject: Quick Update - TechCorp AI Strategy
emails.body: Just wanted to share that TechCorp is doubling down on AI this year. We've hired 50 new ML engineers and are building out our AI Center of Excellence. This aligns perfectly with the kind of partnership we discussed. Excited about the possibilities ahead.
